Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:14.31,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}환상은 있다며
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:14.31,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)\fs35\pos(74,620)}내일
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:16.18,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}눈을 감고서
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:20.50,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}그럼에도 계속해서 걸어나갔지
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:24.17,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}수도 없이 밤을 거듭한대도
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:29.40,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}지울 수가 없어서
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:33.34,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}빛을 갈망하고 있지
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:38.35,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}되돌아본 길로는
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:42.76,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}더는 돌아가지 못한다 할지라도
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:45.58,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}세계는 돌고 돌아
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:50.47,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}기적을 기도한 순간에
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:52.94,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}그 외에는 그 무엇도
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.94,0:23:57.92,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}필요 없어, 이곳에 있는 것은
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:23:59.83,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}「미래」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:23:59.83,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)\fs35\pos(98,620)}소망
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:01.70,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}「희망」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:01.70,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)\fs35\pos(98,620)}소망
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.70,0:24:05.16,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}전하고파
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:07.02,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}상처 입고서
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.02,0:24:08.83,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}상처 입히고서
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.83,0:24:12.54,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}모든 것을 잃는다 할지라도
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.54,0:24:14.36,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}이루어지지 않을
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.36,0:24:16.19,Desir,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}이루고 싶은
